Default exports

By design, the"restrictedNamedExports"option doesn‚Äôt disallowexport defaultdeclarations. If you configure"default"as a restricted name, that restriction will apply only to named export declarations.

Examples of additionalincorrectcode for the"restrictedNamedExports": ["default"]option:

